  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a grill or grill pan to medium-high heat",
    "In a blender or food processor, combine coconut milk, fish sauce, lime juice, brown sugar, coriander seeds, and cumin seeds, and blend until smooth",
    "Add the blended marinade to the trout strips and mix well to coat",
    "Thread the marinated trout strips onto skewers, if using",
    "Brush the grill or grill pan with peanut oil to prevent sticking",
    "Grill the satay for 3-4 minutes per side, or until cooked through",
    "Serve the satay hot, garnished with toasted peanuts and fresh cilantro",
    "Offer with a side of steamed vegetables or a salad for a balanced meal",
    "Refrigerate or freeze any leftovers for up to 3 days"
  ],
